Diagram source for `data-flow.png`. This repository stores Mermaid text here so the pipeline remains reviewable without a binary image renderer.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["CRM"] --> D["Airflow Ingestion"]
    B["Market Intelligence"] --> D
    C["Filings and News"] --> D
    D --> E["Raw Storage"]
    E --> F["Standardized Models"]
    F --> G["Entity Resolution"]
    G --> H["Snowflake / Databricks Marts"]
    G --> I["Neo4j Graph"]
    H --> J["BI and Executive Reporting"]
```
